			<div class="inner">
			
            <p>Avans Machine, Inc., a family owned business, that was established  in 1989.  We started with with three owners and 1,500 sq. ft. facility.  Today, our company is proud to employ 65 workers in our 50,000 sq. ft.  facility.</p>
<p>Avans Machine, Inc. is a precision machine shop that  specializes in CNC Lathe/4th &amp; 5th Axis milling/3-D machining and  all types of general machining.</p>
<p>Our company manufactures a wide range of components used&nbsp;in&nbsp;the following industries:</p>
<ul>
<li>Aerospace and Defense</li>
<li>Commercial and Industrial Equipment</li>
<li>Medical Instruments and Equipment</li>
<li>Medical Implants</li>
<li>Pharmaceutical Equipment</li>
</ul>
